sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ext as External Bank<br/>(external_system)
    participant Client as SOVRClient / curl
    participant Gateway as Protocol API Server<br/>(:3001)
    participant Gate as Health + Provenance Gate
    participant Bus as Command Bus<br/>(7-Stage Pipeline)
    participant Store as Event Store
    participant Proj as Projection Engine
    participant Adapter as ACH Adapter<br/>(Boundary)

    Ext->>Client: 1. POST /identity/session<br/>{actor_type: "external_system"}
    Client->>Gateway: Request JWT
    Gateway-->>Client: JWT + session

    Ext->>Client: 2. POST /capabilities/grant<br/>(governance role)
    Client->>Gateway: Grant treasury.transfer.*
    Gateway->>Store: governance.capability.granted

    Ext->>Client: 3. POST /treasury/transfer_order
    Client->>Gateway: {commandName: "treasury.transfer.request", ...}
    
    Gateway->>Gate: Check HEALTHY + build_hash
    Gate-->>Gateway: OK

    Gateway->>Bus: Submit command

    Bus->>Bus: Stage 1: Identity verification
    Bus->>Bus: Stage 2: Capability + Scope check
    Bus->>Bus: Stage 3: Policy evaluation
    Bus->>Bus: Stage 4: Constitutional (INV-002, INV-003, etc.)
    Bus->>Bus: Stage 5: Execute (reserve + ledger)

    Bus->>Store: treasury.transfer.requested<br/>(21-field envelope)
    Store-->>Bus: Event appended (INV-001)
    Bus->>Proj: Update projections
    Bus->>Store: treasury.transfer.authorized

    Bus->>Gateway: ACCEPTED + events + gates

    Gateway-->>Client: Response with correlation_id

    Note over Ext,Adapter: Async Settlement Path

    Bus->>Adapter: payment.request.create
    Adapter->>Adapter: prepare (ACH)
    Adapter->>Store: payment.rail.prepared

    Adapter->>Adapter: execute
    Adapter->>Store: payment.rail.executed

    Adapter->>Adapter: confirm
    Adapter->>Store: payment.rail.confirmed<br/>+ payment.receipt.issued

    Store->>Proj: Rebuild read models
    Store-->>Consumers: Publish to Kafka / Redis / WS

    Ext->>Client: 4. GET /audit/{correlation_id}
    Client->>Gateway: Query complete trail
    Gateway-->>Ext: Full event chain + isComplete: true
